title: JarExporter causes out of Sync
description: When exporting a directory (project) and placing the exported jar in the same directory (project), an out of sync message is shown when overwriting the exported jar file for the second time.
OB: When exporting a directory and placing the exported jar in the same directory, an out of sync message is displayed when overwriting the exported jar file for the second time.
EB: The out of sync message should not be displayed when overwriting the exported jar file for the second time.
SR:
1. Export a directory (project).
2. Place the exported jar in the same directory (project).
3. Overwrite the exported jar file.
4. Repeat step 3 for the second time.
5. Observe if an out of sync message is displayed.
